#change column date_added from character to date

netflix <- netflix %>% 
  mutate(date_added = mdy(date_added))

##Extracting

netflix %>% 
  mutate(day = day(date_added),
         month = month(date_added, label = TRUE, abbr = FALSE),
         year = year(date_added),
         wday = wday(date_added, label = TRUE))

##Calculating time spans 3 types of time span : - “Difftime” a datetime object that represents days - “Period” represents a timespan like week / month / day - “Duration” represents an exact numebr of seconds

##Subtracting periods from dates

ymd(20200110) + years(1)

[1] "2021-01-09 06:00:00 UTC"
